Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in those days,  \N to travel meant to risk your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:22.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,遭難、追い剥ぎだけでなく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:25.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,怪我や病気も即命取りとなる。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:31.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,旅の途中で消息を絶つことは決して珍しくなかったのである
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:47.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やろうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.29,0:00:51.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やろうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:54.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おや？こいつは…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:20.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この時代、旅とは文字通り命懸けであった。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You could get lost or robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Injuries or illnesses could  \N easily prove fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was not uncommon for travelers to  \N vanish without trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You want...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.29,0:00:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You want...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.98,0:01:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still wanna dance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, one day my passion's fire will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,One day the flames would die out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I thought I didn't need anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But even now, I'm so serious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... but I'm gonna burn it up, baby
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.56,0:01:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling, it's not that easy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But surely it's not that bad either
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby. \NI'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up  \N Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up  \N Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby. \NI'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,#2 The story of Bandai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see. I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How else could you fight a monster \Nlike you just did?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You were so cool. \NYou shouldn't let it go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You could...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you go around slaying monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that sword fixed to your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It fell off your face,  \N and some new skin grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing is fake,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but your new skin is real, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you could see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you don't want to talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah! I'm sorry, I'll get off your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah! Stop, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't eat it raw. Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? Smells good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be even better with salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But this'll do. Here ya go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it seems like \Nyou really can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't hear or talk, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so strange, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to make some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me, and I'll make you rich. \NYou could even be a millionaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so too, \Nthat's why you don't shoo me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru could not see nor hear Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was something  \N he could "see" ever since he was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire of the soul, shall we say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The key was the color.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hostility, hatred,  \N and beings not of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru detected such dangers  \N by their colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as this power, he also possessed  \N superhuman senses and strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This was how he survived the darkness  \N in which he lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru let Dororo stay close,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,only because the color of his soul  \N did not indicate danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. This small one's for me \Nbecause I cooked it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This soul didn't pass him by,  \N but remained close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the second soul to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I say something in my sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you at least tell me your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dororo. Do-ro-ro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess not. You're Mr. No-name then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:07:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I just heard about something \Nthat we could make money with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like there's a monster \Nhaunting a village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Villagers and travelers who stop by \Ndisappear now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to beat it \Nlike you did before and get a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We save people and get money doing it. \NGreat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like a pretty rich village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's really a monster here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did somebody say monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What about a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't assume I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard you're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Got some great news for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:09:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy right here \Nis the best at slaying monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can he really do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As sure as anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the other day, he beat up \Nthis huge monster into little bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So how about it? \NCan't hurt to give us a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Got nothing to lose, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How fortunate that you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll slay it for us, \Nthe village will do much to repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the way you talk, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just filling in for the chief. \NMy name is Denkichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Our chief's name is Bandai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She has injured her legs and can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, please feel free \Nto stay at my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much to offer, \Nbut would you like some supper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like the way you talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is like paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't eaten so much for ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're pretty flashy \Nfor a village troubled by a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have \Na lot of rice paddies, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How do they make so much money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster, right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In front of you, get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:11:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You want...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See? He wants to fight. \NHold on, you'll get what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, take your arm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Hey, it's leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, jeez! It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see the monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but we let it go for today. \NDon't worry, we can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning. Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Bandai wishes to meet you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bandai? Oh yeah, the village chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sorry we haven't even prepared \Nyour breakfast yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That is her residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's really dark in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall light a candle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for being like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't use my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Bandai, the chief of this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have something on my face, child?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's just you're really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for calling you to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about you from the villagers \Nand had to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you might be, and I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it! What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Lady Bandai! \N-He's got a sword for an arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Seize him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, she's no monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-Watch it! \N-Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the boy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them to the storehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck? And you didn't \Ndo anything to last night's monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a kind-looking lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You really can't see, can ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite lively today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to have some companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get caught too, Priest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard there was a monster so I came to \Nsee, and they locked me up in my sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? It could be a clue \Nto where all the people disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyways, \NI've seen you before somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You can see?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We see some things \Npeople with sight can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, it's much more accurate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You see things we can't see?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, you look like \Na clear white flame to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Flame?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your soul, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We see what's on the inside, \Nnot the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Soul? Inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean this Mr. No-name \Ncan see the way you do too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So when he drew his sword back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we can't see anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening? What was that voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like this well \Nis connected to the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Feel that draft?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This place...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's your friend right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you come to attack me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, a sick woman. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up. We only see \Nwhat's inside of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What color?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What I see now is the murky color \Nof blood. The worst color of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too bad I couldn't eat you \Nthe first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've realized it, \Nbut this is something worse than a ghoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's a demon. \N-A demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Bandai, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why'd you let it get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew about it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew, \Nand you fed the travelers to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to, or else it would've eaten up \Nthe villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you wanted us to \Nslay it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If we defeat it, \Nthen your problem's solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like it wasn't Bandai \Nthat he wanted slayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it. You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,To think you were still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be because \N"it" failed to take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"It" was the only one \Nthat couldn't get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you come to get the rest back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting. Let's see if you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Bandai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You want...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, lots of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The money of the travelers \Nyou let Bandai eat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Our village has nothing \Nto make money with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought everything was lost \Nwhen the monster Bandai took over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But the first traveler Lady Bandai ate \Nhad a lot of road money on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And you couldn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? You guys are awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even worse than monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that sound, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that sound what you wanted us to slay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the sound of the bell \Nthat the first traveler carried...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A pilgrim's bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for saying that stuff to you \Nwhen you tried to kill Bandai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who was blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let it get to you. It's natural \Nfor those with sight to be tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Like my dead mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop treating me like a kid, \Nyou No-name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can write?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Priest, what did he write?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hya-kki-maru. So that's your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally know your name. Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I know now, too.  \N No wonder I remember seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you on the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Disquiet by the borders?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they've increased \Nthe number of soldiers on guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As if readying for war.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible. The Sakai Clan are our allies, \Nnot just our neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to investigate something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you in pain? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.05,0:23:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Bandai"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:51.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱ見えてる。どう考えても見えてるって！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁ、見えてるんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:57.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でなきゃバケモンとあんなふうに戦えるわけねぇって！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:03.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すげぇ強かったもんなぁ！\Nその腕、タダで転がしておいちゃもったいねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:05.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんかこう…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:07.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい！おいってば！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いつもああやってバケモン退治してんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:13.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その腕の剣、どうやってついてんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:16.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それからコレ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:19.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたの顔から落ちて、新しい顔が生えた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:22.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こいつはよく見りゃ作りモンだけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:25.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今のアンタの皮は本物…だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:28.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうなってんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:35.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,聞けよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:39.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うん…完全に見えてるだろそれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:43.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんでだよ？オイラと話したくないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:45.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしてだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:48.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わっ！待てよ！ごめん、しつこすぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すげぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わっ！待て待て待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生はよくねぇって！少し待ってなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:41.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほら！うまそうな匂いがしてきたろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:43.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,塩があるといいんだがなぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:46.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まぁ、しょうがねぇ。ほらよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:57.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はぁ…そうしてると本当に見えてねぇって風だよな。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:00.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,耳も聞こえず口も聞けねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ホント不思議なやつだよなぁ、あんた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:05.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まぁいいや…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁ。あんたその腕、金にしねぇか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:18.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらに任せりゃ絶対稼げる。\Nお大尽だって夢じゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:23.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,な？あんただってそう思ってるからおいらを\N追い払わねぇんだ。そうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:27.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸にはどろろの姿も声も届いてはいない。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:32.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが、百鬼丸には生まれながらに見えているものがある
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:36.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,魂の炎、とでも言うほかない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,重要なのは、その色だった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:44.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,敵意、憎悪、またはこの世ならざるもの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:47.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それらの持つ色が百鬼丸に危険を教える
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:54.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,魂の色を見る力。\Nそして、常人ではない間隔と身体能力によって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:59.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸は彼の暗闇の中を生きてきたのである
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:02.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今、百鬼丸がどろろを放っておくのは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:07.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その炎の色が危険ではないからということでしかない。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:08.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:14.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほら、この小さいのはおいらの焼き賃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:19.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,通り過ぎることなく、長く自分のそばに留まる炎は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:21.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,彼にとって2つめだった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:54.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やめろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やめてくれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:01.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら、なんか寝言言ったかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:10.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そっか…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:14.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,聞こえねぇもんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁ、名前くらい教えてくれよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:29.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらはどろろだ。どーろーろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:31.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたは？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:39.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,って、無理か。いいや！もう名無しの権兵衛で。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:41.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おやすみー
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:07:59.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:01.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:06.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,早速あんたの腕で稼げる話を聞いてきた！とにかくちょっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:11.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この先の村にバケモンが出るらしいんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:17.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,村に立ち寄った旅人とか、\N村の人がときどき行方知れずになっちまうらしい。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:21.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そいつをこないだみたいに退治して礼金を貰うんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:25.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人助けしておいらたちも儲かる。な？いい考えだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:40.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,へぇー。なんだか金持ちそうな村だなぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:43.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ホントにバケモンなんか出るのかなぁ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:46.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はて、バケモンとおっしゃいましたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:49.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,化け物がどうかしましたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,へへっ、どうかしたのはこの村だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,知ってるぜ、困ってるって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:57.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いい話を持ってきてやったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:09:02.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんとこのお兄さん！バケモン退治にかけちゃ天下一品。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひとつ頼ってみなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:08.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本当にそんなことができますので？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大出来だよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:15.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こないだもこーんなでけぇバケモンをたーった\N1人で細切れにしちまったのを、
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:16.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,個の目で見たばっかりだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:21.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうよ、頼むだけならタダだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,騙されたと思ってさ、な？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それはもう願ってもないことで。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:31.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,退治していただけるなら、村でできるかぎりのお礼を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:33.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁ、皆の衆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:37.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いやぁ～、話が早いねぇ村長さん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:42.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁいえ、私は名代を務めます伝吉と申す者で…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:45.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,村の長は万代というお方なのですが、
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:48.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なにぶん足を悪くされまして
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:53.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,とにかく、私どものうちをお使いください。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:57.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大したものもございませんが、お食事など…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:00.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おぉっ！いや、ホント話が早いねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:02.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こちらでございます
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:12.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くぅ～、極楽極楽。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:17.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや～、こんなに食べたの久しぶりだぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:23.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でもさ…バケモンに困ってる割に贅沢な暮らししてるよな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:26.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見たとこ大した田んぼもなかったし…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:29.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんで儲けてんだろうなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,出たぁーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:50.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい！そこにいるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:53.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,目の前！こないだみたいにやっつけてくれよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい…何してんだよ、早く！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:11:00.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やろうか…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:03.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほら、やるかって言ってる。待ってろ、今やってやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:06.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,早く…この手、抜かねぇと…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:08.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,早く…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:11.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい、早くしろよ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:15.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,えっ…！おい待て！行っちまうよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,早く…！うぅ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:25.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁもう、何なんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:28.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの…どうかなさいましたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:31.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,化け物は出ましたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:37.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ、いや…出たけど…今日は様子見だ。\Nうん…大したことなかった！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:39.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうでございますか…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:51.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おはようございます。お目覚めでございますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:58.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの…万代さまがお2人にお目にかかりたいと…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,万代？あぁ村長…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:06.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はい、ご朝食も差し上げず申し訳ありませんが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:08.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいよ。わかった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:15.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あちらの屋敷でございます
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:17.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すげぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:24.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,では
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:27.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何だい、ずいぶん暗いな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:29.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今、灯りを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:34.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このようなお見苦しい姿、お許しを…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,足を患っておりますので
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:41.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私がこの村の長、万代でございます
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:45.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊や、私の顔に何か？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:48.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,い…いや、綺麗だなぁって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:51.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,フ…恐れ入ります。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:54.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お呼び立てして申し訳ございません。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:58.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,村人の話を聞いてどうしてもお会いしなければ、と…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:01.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,特に、そこのお方。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:04.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もしやと思っておりましたが、やはり…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:06.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,え？知ってるのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:16.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何をなさいます？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:18.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい、何するつもりだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:20.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この人は人間だぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待て…やめろ！どうしたんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:26.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,万代さま！\N-こいつ腕から剣が生えてやがる！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,早く取り押さえろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:31.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やめろ、あの人はバケモンじゃない…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:32.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おやめください！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:34.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待てぇ！\N動くんじゃねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:35.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そいつも仲間だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:36.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,離せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,土蔵へ連れて行け！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:58.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どういうことだよ！\Nゆんべのバケモンには指一本動かさねぇで…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:02.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんな優しそうな人にいきなり斬りかかろうとしてさぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:05.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わかったよ！あんたホンット見えてねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんも見えてねぇんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:11.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ずいぶんと賑やかだねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:15.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お仲間ができて嬉しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:19.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何だい？坊さん。あんたも捕まってんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:25.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バケモンが出るってんで見物に来たら、\N寝てる間に連れ込まれちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:26.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:32.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さぁてね…案外これが行方知れずの種明かしかもしれないねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:37.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それより、お前さんには見覚えがある
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:40.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見覚えって…目、見えるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:46.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あたしらには、目明きには見えないものが見えたりするんでねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:50.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そっちのほうがよっぽど確かだったりすることもあるのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:53.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何だよ、見えないものが見えるって？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:58.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,例えば今あたしにゃ、お前さんが綺麗な真っ白い炎に見える
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,炎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:02.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,言ってみりゃ、魂さね。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:06.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見てくれじゃない、中身が見えるのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:09.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,魂…中身…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:14.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ、もしかしてこの名無しの権兵衛も坊さんみたいに見えるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:16.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,かもしれないねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:19.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,じゃあ、さっき刀抜いたのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今度は何だよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:23.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,気をつけ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:25.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,妙な気配だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:33.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わっ！なんも見えねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:36.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫、あたしらには同じことさ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:49.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうなったんだ、今の声なんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいからついておいで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:56.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうやらこの井戸は外に通じているらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見えねぇよぉ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:00.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いやーっ！怖いー！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:03.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫。ほら、外の風だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:06.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれ？ここって…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あそこにお連れがいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:13.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ…また私を斬りにいらしたのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:16.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このような病人を一体なぜ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:21.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,無駄だよ。あたしらにはお前さんの中身しか見えないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:23.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,色は？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:24.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうさねぇ…今見えてるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:30.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どす黒い血のような赤。最悪の色だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:33.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さっき食いそこなったのは惜しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:48.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わかってるだろうな。\Nそんなやつは化け物なんて可愛いもんじゃない！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:52.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神だ\N-鬼神？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:01.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,痛くねぇのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:12.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,万代さま！お逃げください！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:20.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい！なんでバケモン逃がすんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:22.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どういうつもりだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:25.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前さん、知っていなすったな？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:28.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,知ってて旅人を食わせてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:33.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうしなければ、あの化け物は村の者を食らいますんで…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:37.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だからおいらたちに退治してほしかったんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:40.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あいつを倒せばそれで解決じゃねぇか！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:45.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうやら退治してほしかったのは万代じゃなかったようで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:21.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,間違いない…お前は！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:24.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よもや生きていようとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:29.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アレが奪いそこなった、そのせいか。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:33.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アレだけがお前を取れなかった…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,残りを取り戻す気か？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:40.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,面白い、できるものなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:43.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁっ…万代さまぁっ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:54.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やろうかぁ…？やろうかぁ…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:55.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あいつ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:05.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだこれ、大金だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:06.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すげぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:10.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,万代に食わせた旅人の金だね？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,えっ？どういうことだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:16.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うちの村は他に稼げるネタもなくて…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:21.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,化け物の万代さまに乗っ取られたときはもう終わりかと…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:27.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも最初に万代さまが食った旅人がかなりの路銀を持ってたもんで…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:30.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,味を占めちまったってわけだね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:34.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何だよ！それ最低じゃねぇか！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:36.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バケモンよりもっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:42.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ぐわぁっ…！止めてくれ！あの音を…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:47.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前さんが退治してほしかったのはあれかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:52.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,最初に路銀を奪った旅人が持ってた…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:56.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お遍路だったんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:06.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,悪かったよ。万代斬ろうとしたあんたにひどいこと言って…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:08.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見えてなかったのはおいらだった…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,聞こえてねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:14.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,案外気持ちは通じるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:19.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,気にすることはない。目が見えてるもんなら、騙されて当然さ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:23.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,っていうか、似てたんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:27.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死んだおっかちゃんに、似てた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:31.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうかい…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,な…なんだよ急に！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:53.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ガキ扱いすんな！名無し野郎のくせに！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:57.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだ？字が書けるのか…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:01.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊さん！なんて書いてあるのかわかるかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:04.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どれ、触れさせてくれるかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:14.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひゃっ…き…まる…あんたの名前だね？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:16.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,へぇー、百鬼丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:21.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ははっ、やっとわかった。百鬼丸か
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:26.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私もわかったよ。見覚えがあるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:38.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前さん…あんときの…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:43.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何？国境に不穏な動きだと？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:47.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ。警護に当たる兵の数が増えております。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:49.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦の準備ではと思われ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:53.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,馬鹿な！隣国の堺殿とは同盟の間柄…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:00.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そちに探ってもらうことがある
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:15.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしたんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:18.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい！痛いのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:21.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁ！大丈夫かよ！しっかりしろよ、おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:24.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしたんだよ…なぁ！
